  description: The Assassin Creed franchise is a action adventure game about a struggle
    between 2 factions and the story revolves around the protagonist trapped in this
    conflict. There are quite a few installments, but some noted that the game is
    increasing focusing on representation at the expense of the story. In particular,
    many cited that the male characters across new installments are written to be
    more emotional.
